{"tid":1064373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新西蘭恐襲：歸咎回教移民　澳洲議員被掟雞蛋","createTime":"2019-03-16T13:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:07:44.000Z","uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"494b3ce911be2ddce6cb2bd238989de174b5b7d5","tid":1064373,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"澳洲極右參議員安寧（Fraser Anning）周五（15日）發表不當言論，把新西蘭基督城清真寺恐襲，歸咎於該國接收太多狂熱回教徒所致。他翌日在墨爾本出席活動時被人投擲雞蛋，總理莫里森直斥安寧的言論「嘔心」，認為他應感到羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n屬凱特澳洲人黨（Katter's Australian Party）的安寧指新西蘭移民法案接收不少回教徒，導致慘劇發生，他批評左翼政客及傳媒把事件歸咎槍械管制寬鬆，認為說法老套。安寧周六（16日）出席一個記者會時，被一名年輕男子從後用雞蛋擲向頭部，他即時揮拳及腳踢還擊，警員其後帶走涉事男子。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森回應稱：「參議員安寧將是次可怕的恐襲，與移民及回教信仰混為一談，對此我予以譴責。」他又指該言論令人不安及震驚，在澳洲站不住腳，政府將於國會內提出譴責動議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f0_Wnh_zEbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff0_Wnh_zEbU&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=70d98dea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f0_Wnh_zEbU</a>"},{"pid":"08933b1078fd4a031bd0eea5d3bbbe795d4759a2","tid":1064373,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43a8898c8cbeffd2aa6389aa2e1079d8c5bd2a8","tid":1064373,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08933b1078fd4a031bd0eea5d3bbbe795d4759a2","tid":1064373,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231078bdcc964788d8dd4233104a55616b9aed2","tid":1064373,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"「參議員安寧將是次可怕的恐襲，與移民及回教信仰混為一談，對此我予以譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrXh5YS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrXh5YS.png&h=97ce2074&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}